{
  "texts": [
    "The combination of both components is represented by C(D, M).",
    "Experimental ResultsThe dataset used in this research comprises real-world sensor data collected from a WSN deployed in an industrial environment called the WSN-IndFeat [27].",
    "It includes diverse features, labeled anomalies, and realtime streaming data, making it a practical resource for developing robust detection solutions tailored to industrial scenarios.",
    "The WSN consists of a network of interconnected sensor nodes, each equipped with various sensors to measure environmental parameters such as temperature, humidity, pressure, voltage level, and motion.",
    "The dataset contains a time series of sensor readings captured at regular intervals from these nodes."
  ]
}